- **Rules:** 65–75ch line length; supports 200% text scaling; avoid ALL-CAPS in paragraphs; ensure ≥4.5:1 contrast.

**CSS starter**

```css
@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Flex:wght@400;500;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap");
html {
  font-family: "Roboto Flex", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-synthesis: none;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
}
h1,
h2,
h3 {
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  color: #111;
}
p {
  max-width: 70ch;
  color: #333;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
```

---

## 5) Elevation & Motion

- **Shadows:** e1 `0 1px 2px rgba(11,12,16,.10)`, e2 `0 4px 10px rgba(11,12,16,.20)`, e3 `0 8px 24px rgba(11,12,16,.30)`.
- **Dark-mode glow:** `0 0 0 2px rgba(99,102,241,.35)` on focus/active.
- **Motion:** Framer Motion; micro (150–200ms), modal (250–300ms), respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.

/ CTAs             | 600 uppercase | 1.0        | 1.2         | Compact, assertive call-to-action style. |

All sizes use fluid scaling with `clamp()` to adapt between mobile and desktop viewports.

